{"id":136660,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/02/简讯：巴林国王委派王储开展对话/","date":"2011-02-19T13:30:23Z","modified":"2011-02-19T13:30:23Z","title":"简讯：巴林国王委派王储开展对话","content":"<div>\n<p>巴林国王哈马德委派王储萨拉曼与全国各党派开展对话，谋求解决日益恶化的政治危机。</p>\n<p>然而，首都麦纳麦的混乱局面仍然持续。入夜后，反政府示威者持续与保安部队冲突，市面仍可听见枪声。</p>\n<p>星期五早些时候，示威者企图操向市中心的珍珠广场，军队开枪打伤了至少50人。</p>\n<p>在麦纳麦采访的BBC记者指出，属于伊斯兰逊尼派的王室现在提出对话试图安抚以什叶派为主的示威者，或许为时已晚。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ZfsMW0-p9HINT3bivF3yBx4-CSs/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ZfsMW0-p9HINT3bivF3yBx4-CSs/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ZfsMW0-p9HINT3bivF3yBx4-CSs/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/ZfsMW0-p9HINT3bivF3yBx4-CSs/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=O_XkjLNr4A4:CDNQECeUz5E:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=O_XkjLNr4A4:CDNQECeUz5E:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=O_XkjLNr4A4:CDNQECeUz5E:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=O_XkjLNr4A4:CDNQECeUz5E:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=O_XkjLNr4A4:CDNQECeUz5E:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=O_XkjLNr4A4:CDNQECeUz5E:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/O_XkjLNr4A4\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>需翻墙软件请发电邮(最好用Gmai